pokemoncobbled.move.tackle.desc: A physical attack in which the user charges and slams into the target with its whole body.
pokemoncobbled.move.aerial_ace.desc: The user confounds the target with speed, then slashes. This attack never misses.
pokemoncobbled.move.air_slash.desc: The user attacks with a blade of air that slices even the sky. This may also make the target flinch.
pokemoncobbled.move.aura_sphere.desc: The user lets loose a blast of aura power from deep within its body at the target. This attack never misses.
